dc_title_s: Aeromagnetic anomaly map of Minnesota, S-11
dc_description_s: Aeromagnetic anomaly (total magnetic intensity anomaly (relative to the earth's magnetic field, interpretation of magnetic data collected from airborne surveys, the map colors indicate the distribution and concentration of magnetic minerals (primarily iron-bearing) within the upper crust of the earth) map of Minnesota, scale 1:3,168,000.
